  <summary>5/18/1995--Introduced.
Prohibits funds from being appropriated to the Department of Defense for any fiscal year after 1995 for procurement, military construction, or research, development, test, and evaluation for: (1) the Army Commanche helicopter; (2) certain Navy fighter and attack aircraft; (3) the Navy New Attack Submarine; (4) Marine Corps V-22 Osprey aircraft; (5) Air Force F-22 fighter aircraft; (6) the MILSTAR communications satellite; and (7) any ballistic missile defense program carried out through the Ballistic Missile Defense Organization.</summary>
